headline: Is Medtronic Still Attractively Priced After Its Strong 2025 Share Price Rally?
summary: If you are wondering whether Medtronic is still a solid buy at around $101 a share, or if the easy money has already been made, you are in the right place to unpack what the current price really implies. Despite slipping 3.8% over the last week, the stock is still up 12.1% over the past month, 26.4% year to date, and 24.6% over the last year, which has put valuation firmly back in the spotlight.
